Class SetPackage

  • Object
    • Item
      • SetPackage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class SetPackage
extends Item
    Stores information about a single setPackage, particularly used in context of a menu. This class stores the name, price, description of setPackage Menu. various methods to add new alaCartes/setPackages and remove existing alaCartes/setPackages.
    Author:
    Liu Liling
